About


&lt;h2&gt;Current Role&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;div class="role-card"&gt;
    &lt;div class="role-header"&gt;
        &lt;div class="role-title"&gt;Product Manager - Biomarker Module Development&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="expand-icon"&gt;▶&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="role-brief"&gt;
        Leading development of biomarker modules for omics research, working at the intersection of computational biology and AI-driven drug discovery.
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="role-responsibilities"&gt;
        &lt;strong style="color: #00d4ff; font-size: 1.05rem;"&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;
        &lt;ul&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Spearheading biomarker module development and integration across multiple research platforms&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Extracting and curating data from public databases using advanced LLM models (Llama and Gemini)&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Implementing scripting-based approaches to streamline data curation workflows&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Contributing to cross-functional module development by incorporating biomarkers as key features&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Optimizing LLM prompts and evaluating model accuracy to enhance AI/ML pipeline performance&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;Collaborating closely with data engineers and data scientists to build innovative solutions&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;





Professional Experience


&lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-year"&gt;2024 - Present&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-title"&gt;Product Manager - Biomarker Module&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-company"&gt;Pune, India&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-description"&gt;
            Leading development of biomarker modules for omics research. Collaborating with data engineers and scientists to integrate AI/ML approaches.
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-details"&gt;
            &lt;ul&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Spearheading biomarker module development and integration across multiple research platforms&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Utilizing LLM models (Llama, Gemini) for automated data extraction from public databases&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Implementing scripting-based approaches to streamline data curation workflows&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Optimizing LLM prompts and evaluating model accuracy to enhance AI/ML pipeline performance&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-dot"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-year"&gt;2022 - 2024&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-title"&gt;Associate Scientific Manager&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-company"&gt;Pune, India&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-description"&gt;
            Led data curation for AI/ML-powered drug discovery modules in an agile, cross-functional environment.
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-details"&gt;
            &lt;div class="timeline-achievements"&gt;
                &lt;strong&gt;Key Achievements:&lt;/strong&gt;
                &lt;ul&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Enhanced LLM model performance through strategic prompt optimization and accuracy evaluation&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Streamlined data curation processes for multiple AI/ML modules&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Bridged the gap between scientific expertise and technical implementation&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Collaborated with product managers, data engineers, and data scientists&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-dot"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-year"&gt;2019 - 2022&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-title"&gt;Associate Biomedical Scientist&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-company"&gt;Precision Biomarker Laboratories, Cedars-Sinai Medical Center, Los Angeles, CA&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-description"&gt;
            Conducted R&D in clinical proteomics and biomarker discovery, driving improvements in laboratory workflows.
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-details"&gt;
            &lt;div class="timeline-achievements"&gt;
                &lt;strong&gt;Key Achievements:&lt;/strong&gt;
                &lt;ul&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Developed novel PTMomics platforms for post-translational modification analysis&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Supervised laboratory technicians and managed end-to-end project delivery&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Improved existing workflows through collaborative innovation&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Led study execution, report compilation, and stakeholder presentations&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-dot"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-year"&gt;2017 - 2019&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-title"&gt;Postdoctoral Fellow&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-company"&gt;University of Southern Denmark&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-description"&gt;
            Developed comprehensive pipeline for identifying post-translationally modified biomarkers in clinical samples.
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-details"&gt;
            &lt;ul&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Worked with Prof. Martin R. Larsen on cutting-edge proteomics research&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Advanced the field of clinical proteomics through innovative methodologies&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Published research in high-impact scientific journals&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-dot"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;





Education


&lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-year"&gt;2012 - 2017&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-title"&gt;PhD in Biochemistry&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-company"&gt;University of Turku, Finland&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-description"&gt;
            Conducted research under Prof. Riitta Lahesmaa and Dr. Robert Moulder focusing on proteomics applications in clinical research.
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-details"&gt;
            &lt;div class="timeline-achievements"&gt;
                &lt;strong&gt;Research Focus:&lt;/strong&gt;
                &lt;ul&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Identified and validated serum protein biomarkers for Type 1 diabetes&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Investigated protein biomarkers for carotid atherosclerosis&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Applied mass spectrometry-based proteomics to clinical samples&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li&gt;Developed computational methods for biomarker validation&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-dot"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-year"&gt;2010 - 2012&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-title"&gt;Master's Degree&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-company"&gt;National Chemical Laboratory (NCL), India&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-description"&gt;
            Completed master's thesis in proteomics and mass spectrometry, establishing foundation for research career.
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-details"&gt;
            &lt;ul&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Worked under joint supervision of Drs. Mahesh J. Kulkarni and B. Santhakumari&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Gained expertise in advanced proteomics techniques&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Published research findings in peer-reviewed journals&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-dot"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="timeline-item"&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-content"&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-year"&gt;Bachelor's&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-title"&gt;Pharmacy Degree&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-company"&gt;India&lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-description"&gt;
            Pharmacist by training, providing strong foundation in pharmaceutical sciences.
        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;div class="timeline-details"&gt;
            &lt;ul&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Strong foundation in pharmaceutical sciences and drug development principles&lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;li&gt;Comprehensive understanding of medicinal chemistry and pharmacology&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;/ul&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="timeline-dot"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;





&lt;h2&gt;Expertise&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style="margin: 1.5rem 0;"&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Mass Spectrometry Proteomics&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;PTM Analysis&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Biomarker Discovery&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Large Language Models&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;AI/ML Pipeline&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Data Curation&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Computational Biology&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Omics Analysis&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Professional Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style="margin: 1.5rem 0;"&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Product Management&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Cross-functional Collaboration&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Project Leadership&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Agile Methodology&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Scientific Communication&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="skill-item"&gt;Prompt Engineering&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;





&lt;h2&gt;Career Journey&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My career represents a unique evolution from bench scientist to AI-driven drug discovery leader. Starting with hands-on proteomics research during my PhD and postdoc, I developed deep expertise in mass spectrometry, biomarker discovery, and computational analysis.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;At Cedars-Sinai Medical Center, I translated this research expertise into clinical applications, developing new platforms and improving laboratory workflows.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Today, I leverage this scientific foundation to lead biomarker module development, integrating cutting-edge AI/ML technologies with proteomics knowledge to accelerate drug discovery. This journey has equipped me with a rare combination of deep scientific expertise and practical AI/ML implementation skills, positioning me at the forefront of computational biology and pharmaceutical innovation.&lt;/p&gt;
